snippet.title: Bzzzt Game – Official Launch Trailer (Long)
snippet.description:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1293170/Bzzzt/
https://www.gog.com/en/game/bzzzt

The BZZZT game is finally out!!!

The Bzzzt game has be released on Steam, GoG and Epic Store on November 13!

Bzzzt is a fast-paced "jump-dash-run" retro game with a fresh and modern design made almost single-handedly by one solo developer, Karel Matejka, known as Ko.dll.

Be ready for pleasant challenges, beautiful pixel art, more than 50 stages, intense boss fights and a catchy soundtrack!

#pixelart #pixelartist #pixelartgame #solodev #indiegame #madewithunity #steamgame #bzzzt
